                    <img src="https://discover.castlebranch.com/CBBridges/images/cb-icon-pro-advantage-tracker.png" alt="customized" width="193px" style="margin: 30px 0px;">
                    <p class="lead">輕量化追蹤，資料不再眼花撩亂</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="feature_3" class="bg-danger mr-md-3 px-3 px-md-5 text-center text-light overflow-hidden">
                <div class="my-3 py-3">
                    <h2 class="display-5">CRM行銷自動化</h2>
                    <img src="https://trevisantecnologia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/connection.png" alt="crm-automation" width="412px">
